Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Unhone kaha tha — kitchen mein mat aana. Aaj main apni kitchen ki queen hoon.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.30,0:00:05.93,Overlay,,0,0,0,,Kitchen mein mat aana...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaadi ke baad jab main sasural aayi, sapne the hazaaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lekin saas ne pehle din hi clear kar diya — yeh kitchen mera hai, tum mat aana.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.55,0:00:18.18,Overlay,,0,0,0,,Yeh kitchen MERA hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Raat ko akele room mein phone pe recipes dekhti thi. Aankhen bheegi, par hausla pakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chupke chupke tiffin banana shuru kiya. Pehle 5 customers, phir 50.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.80,0:00:30.43,Overlay,,0,0,0,,5 customers... phir 50
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ek saal mein mera catering business lakhon ka ho gaya. Sab kehte the — Priya ka khaana magic hai.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.93,0:00:36.56,Overlay,,0,0,0,,PRIYA'S KITCHEN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Phir woh din aaya. Saas mere restaurant ke bahar khadi thi. Ghar ka paisa khatam ho gaya tha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maine unka haath pakda aur kaha — Aaiye, ab yeh kitchen humara hai. Kuch darvaze band hote hain taake hum apna ghar bana sakein.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.18,0:00:48.81,Overlay,,0,0,0,,Ab yeh kitchen HUMARA hai.
